Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,==========OP===========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.74,0:00:39.01,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}頑な心のままで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.01,0:00:42.40,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}石ころはどこまで行ける
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.40,0:00:45.76,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}砂のように脆く崩れる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.76,0:00:49.08,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}一文字も読めない未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.08,0:00:51.34,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}don't believe in action
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.34,0:00:55.56,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}ただ前に進むだけじゃ見えない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.56,0:00:57.91,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}show me your emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.91,0:01:05.29,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,666)}言葉の出来ないものを下さい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.55,0:01:08.86,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}一粒の冷たい石に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.86,0:01:12.20,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}秘められた熱もあるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:15.56,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}どうせなら 勝ちに行きたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.56,0:01:18.94,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}何もかも見えない未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.94,0:01:21.15,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}you are my illusion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.15,0:01:25.48,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}空っぽのままの心でもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.48,0:01:27.77,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,666)}show me your addiction
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.77,0:01:31.56,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}閉ざされた夢を探して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.56,0:01:35.35,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}勢い任せで掴んだ手が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.35,0:01:38.61,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}きっと君を変えてくsignal
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.61,0:01:41.38,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}会いたくて 飛んだって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.38,0:01:45.24,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(120,266)}堕ちてゆくけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.24,0:01:48.56,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}もう一度 空を目指して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.56,0:01:51.88,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}放り投げる想いすべて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:54.72,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}泣いだって 分け合って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.72,0:01:57.74,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}君が笑うまで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.74,0:02:02.98,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,866)}stone cold
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.96,0:00:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.74,0:00:39.01,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}以一颗顽固的心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.01,0:00:42.40,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}石块可以去往任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.40,0:00:45.76,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}如同砂土般轻易崩坏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.76,0:00:49.08,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}无法预知一字的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.08,0:00:51.34,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}don't believe in action
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.34,0:00:55.56,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}如若只是一味向前则会迷失所有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.56,0:00:57.91,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}show me your emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.91,0:01:05.29,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,666)}请赐予我无法用语言形容的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.55,0:01:08.86,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}一颗冰冷的石头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.86,0:01:12.20,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}恐怕也隐藏著炙热的温度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:15.56,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}既然已经决定 那就想要取得胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.56,0:01:18.94,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}空无一物的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.94,0:01:21.15,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}you are my illusion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.15,0:01:25.48,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}就算只有一颗空洞的心也没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.48,0:01:27.77,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,666)}show me your addiction
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.77,0:01:31.56,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}追寻紧闭的梦境
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.56,0:01:35.35,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}把一切交给气势 握紧的双手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.35,0:01:38.61,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}绝对能够改变你的人生signal
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.61,0:01:41.38,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}如此思念你 哪怕就算飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.38,0:01:45.24,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(120,266)}也终会坠落消失
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.24,0:01:48.56,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}再一次冲上天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.56,0:01:51.88,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}抱紧所有抛下的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:54.72,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}就算哭泣 也一起承担
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.72,0:01:57.74,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}直到你微笑的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.74,0:02:02.98,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,866)}stone cold



