Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,==========TEXT==========
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.69,0:03:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到0号了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.74,0:03:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在Arachne正在追击中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.74,0:03:52.73,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arachne：希腊神话中的纺织高手 挑战雅典娜失败 下场很悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cyclopes需要进行再调整
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:56.65,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cyclopes：希腊神话中的独眼巨人 X战警的队长 某某高达中某某基地下面的自爆装置等等都引用于此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.74,0:03:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.27,0:04:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为原石品质的低劣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.43,0:04:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给外部带来了影响
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.52,0:04:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.78,0:04:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要比现在的等级更高的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.90,0:04:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有他们的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 还没有那个必要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.30,0:04:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.72,0:04:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到治疗的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不注射这种药的话 你就会变成怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然因为副作用会有点痛 不过你就忍忍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么请开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.19,0:05:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.36,0:05:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从我身上提取出来的血清
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.94,0:06:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么太大的效果
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.94,0:06:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再这样乱来会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.68,0:06:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果没有血清的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈特就会变成真正的恶石
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制造浓度更高的血清
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.91,0:06:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从蓝羽…琉璃身上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.85,0:06:27.41,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天从课本185页开始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.43,0:06:34.28,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是关于上节课里被称为现代经济史一环的国富论
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.77,0:06:38.54,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国富论就如上节课所教的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手里剑？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镜？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.65,0:06:40.10,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是由亚当·斯密所著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:43.01,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对现代社会的经济史产生了巨大影响的一本书
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.69,0:06:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午休时能一起吃便当吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.10,0:06:46.85,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最有名的是「无形的手」这一概念
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.65,0:06:56.16,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚当·斯密认为人们就算自由地进行生产活动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.08,0:06:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.55,0:07:04.24,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社会不仅不会陷入混乱 反而会走上和谐繁荣的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.92,0:07:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也做了有马同学的那份  琉璃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.43,0:07:07.85,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后课本的186页
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:12.83,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,则是亚当·斯密阐述其中政府的职责充其量就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.39,0:07:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.14,0:07:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹童子同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去一下洗手间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢…慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.54,0:07:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来想叫你一声的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.29,0:07:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过看你还在睡觉就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很担心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.96,0:07:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你一直没回教室
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:07:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微…什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.01,0:08:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好近！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.57,0:08:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…总是靠得很近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.07,0:08:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离…我们俩说话时候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.31,0:08:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我说话的时候 能不能保持1米的距离啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.80,0:08:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 有马同学果然还是喜欢一个人独处吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.80,0:08:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不是 也不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是还没习惯这种样子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.33,0:08:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么要不要特训一下啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.81,0:08:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如我就这样住进有马同学的家里之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.40,0:08:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.66,0:08:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就一个人吃便当吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.22,0:08:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.38,0:08:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你无所谓吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.57,0:08:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我吃掉两人份的便当然后变胖也无所谓？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…真是麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.39,0:08:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦？是在说我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:08:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我不是那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 那我去别的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.41,0:09:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.37,0:09:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…真的走了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…或许真的有点烦人啊

Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.66,0:09:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你变成大美人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得 像这样一直打磨石头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:10:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种迈入老年的感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.79,0:10:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 就好像一边喝著粗茶 一边坐在走廊上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.86,0:10:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想将来…你说对吧 镜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.95,0:10:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.07,0:10:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为一起坐著的肯定是我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 镜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 镜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.95,0:10:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有非常麻烦的微笑凑过来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.50,0:10:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.54,0:10:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐 石头的打磨这样就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.61,0:10:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.77,0:10:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有些心事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了镜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.99,0:10:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不懂怎么打磨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.51,0:10:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果说一声的话 我明明就会来教你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:10:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:07.22,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你到底在装什么内行啊 我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.87,0:11:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 丹童子同学没有来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.85,0:11:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.74,0:11:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹童子同学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.51,0:11:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为个子太高
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.89,0:11:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一不在的话 感觉就像是没有了大佛的镰仓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.54,0:11:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.08,0:11:18.63,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也没打磨到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:20.90,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 早就打磨到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:22.52,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没打磨到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:23.82,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长你不担心他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.58,0:11:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹童子同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.94,0:11:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 每个人都有自己的事情要忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过分干涉也不太好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.66,0:11:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许又去河边捡石头了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.77,0:11:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊 我很烦人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.46,0:11:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐 时间差不多到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.38,0:11:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,财团的例行理事会议
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经都这时候了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.67,0:11:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镜同学已经要回去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.30,0:11:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非…非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.13,0:11:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.02,0:11:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也没办法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我们就先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.62,0:12:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.79,0:12:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说若菜啊 既然镜同学已经回去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直截了当的说 我们可以回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.29,0:12:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话 今天多亏了有理事会议才得救啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 只是一味打磨石头的工作真让人受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.96,0:12:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说这世上有很多事情让人无法忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.84,0:12:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只有那个 都能让我开始怀疑自己生存的意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.54,0:12:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能让你大肆抱怨 看来极其麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个实在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,极其让人受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是一个很麻烦的女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:12:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.44,0:13:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差点就要碎了啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.85,0:13:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 只是稍微擦到了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.28,0:13:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有哪里觉得痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.04,0:13:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上去医院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.84,0:13:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用 我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.37,0:13:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃 琉璃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有恶石的气息啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.51,0:13:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要对琉璃做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.23,0:13:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.21,0:13:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就跳出来 真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您费心了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.77,0:13:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你 真伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.53,0:13:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.04,0:13:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没事的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.91,0:14:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.17,0:14:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快找到大小姐在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.97,0:14:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位没有在一起吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一不留神她就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.93,0:14:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在大小姐的手机没有讯号
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GPS以及各感应器都没有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.34,0:14:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.26,0:14:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联络区县警署
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.95,0:14:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要求紧急搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.97,0:14:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.85,0:14:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.30,0:14:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研美先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.55,0:14:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.89,0:14:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝羽琉璃失踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.29,0:14:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃酱她？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是辉岛奈特吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.31,0:14:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.91,0:14:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能出动Cyclopes吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.51,0:14:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在调整中…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:14:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.66,0:15:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是您身体状况也不太好…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.85,0:15:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢货！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.27,0:15:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝羽财团陷入危机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.75,0:15:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我不出动的话还有谁会出动？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果奈特拐走了琉璃酱的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.64,0:15:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他下一个接触对象一定就是丹童子君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.71,0:15:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.17,0:15:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就看准这点出击吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.74,0:15:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arachne能出动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.58,0:15:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.28,0:15:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也会来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.15,0:15:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹童子 大小姐失踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.13,0:15:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.16,0:15:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.47,0:15:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.15,0:15:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬间就消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.80,0:16:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 就在我稍微下车的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.03,0:16:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手机呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.33,0:16:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接不通
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.59,0:16:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镜先生 搜查的准备做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 我马上过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.42,0:16:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.93,0:16:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就别来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是和恶石有关的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.63,0:16:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你过来只能成为累赘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.05,0:16:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什么事的话我会联络你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.05,0:16:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.48,0:16:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是不是看到了什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 我去别的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.95,0:16:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她不在了我会怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.68,0:17:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成恶石的话不就无法恢复了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.07,0:17:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊我！只考虑自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.41,0:17:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太差劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.99,0:17:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.74,0:17:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能依靠这家伙了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.41,0:17:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 还活著吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.52,0:17:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.19,0:17:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复活了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.83,0:17:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.94,0:17:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么在你家啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.56,0:17:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊 你还记得你被劈成两半了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.86,0:17:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊鬼？我感觉到了恶石的气息…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶石？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝羽同学是被恶石拐走了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.69,0:17:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被拐走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.12,0:17:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你 琉璃被拐走了吗啊鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.79,0:18:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是来问你这个的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.63,0:18:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直不知道蓝羽同学在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.72,0:18:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.54,0:18:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个气息是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.09,0:18:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这个气息是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.47,0:18:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈特啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈特？辉岛奈特？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.97,0:18:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心一点啊鬼 他就在附近啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙 是研美的走狗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是狗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.56,0:18:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别来妨碍我！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.50,0:18:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.86,0:19:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研美先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来一时难分高下的样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.29,0:19:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.01,0:19:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来应该是由我出击的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.49,0:19:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的SP现在正在抓捕辉岛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.00,0:19:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辉岛奈特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.46,0:19:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么没发现啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他们拐走了大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.10,0:19:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得很让人生气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.97,0:20:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.65,0:20:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶石的气息消失了啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.49,0:20:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 来了来了 丰满小妞来了啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.05,0:20:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.80,0:20:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.32,0:20:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.96,0:21:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 这下事态更严重了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.32,0:21:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点把琉璃酱从他们手中救出的话 她就很危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙恐怕是想从琉璃酱身上提取血清
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血清？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.06,0:21:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 只要有那个的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.42,0:21:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈特就算处于恶石状态也能保持正常理智
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.94,0:21:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过如果要持续提取那个的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.71,0:21:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙恐怕就再也不会释放琉璃酱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.99,0:21:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.63,0:21:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有马
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她不在 你也很担心自身安危吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.10,0:21:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你不用担心自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的研究所里也有血清
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.57,0:21:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一有什么情况 你来我的研究所使用血清就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.13,0:21:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是蓝羽同学再也回不来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.30,0:21:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.62,0:21:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以为此我们现在要竭尽全力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.22,0:21:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个东西安装好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.62,0:21:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.66,0:22:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您指什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.50,0:22:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他身上安装了发信器
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.01,0:22:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻准备进行追击吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.33,0:22:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.69,0:22:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝羽同学
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.08,0:22:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 我需要新的血液

